      "type": "SET_CONTENT",
      "input": {
        "content": "# network-profile model represents network-level organizational entities\n\n`powerhouse/network-profile` (11 ops) represents top-level organizational entities like DAOs or ecosystem networks. Part of the Organization & Identity zone.\n\n## Position in Ecosystem\n\nOrganization & Identity zone. Likely the parent organizational context for [[builder-profile model describes individual contributor identities]] and [[operational-hub-profile model defines operational hub configurations]].\n\n---\n\nTopics:\n- [[ecosystem map]]\n- [[object relations]]",
